<span id="freeTextContainer6070677106147059362">I&apos;m sure the advice in this book will be useful for some, but I couldn&apos;t get past the use of a casual jokes trivializing the genocide of Native Americans and mocking autistic children. I&apos;m not interested in learning writing from an author who hasn&apos;t progress passed humor and metaphors founded on ignorance and bigotry.</span>
