<li class='cover' id='bookCover_44905'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/44905.Writing_Down_the_Bones"><img alt="Writing Down the Bones: Freeing the Writer Within" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1386924733l/44905._SX98_.jpg" />
